                                                          (* ; "Edited 23-Feb-89 10:59 by krivacic")

(* ;;; "fgh 5/23/86 Renamed to NC.OpenNoteFile from NC.OpenDatabaseFile.  Total revamp to implement device vector.")

(* ;;; 
