                                                                           FullFileName 
                                                                           " failed because " 
                                                                           ReturnValue "."
                                                                           (CHARACTER 13]
                                        (RETURN ReturnValue]
          
          (* * Run through CloseNoteFileFns with param of AFTER.
          Stop if any returns DON'T)

                    [for Function in NC.CloseNoteFileFns thereis (EQ 'DON'T (APPLY* Function NoteFile
                                                                                   'AFTER]
          
