          NC.OrigReadTable])

(NC.ReadPropList
  [LAMBDA (NoteFileOrStream)                                 (* rht%: " 1-Nov-86 15:12")
          
          (* * Get a prop list off of the file.)
          
          (* * rht 1/23/86%: Now takes notefile or stream as arg.)
          
          (* * rht 11/1/86%: Now uses our readtable when reading.)

